question: Within a radius of 50 kilometers, what café is available located en route to the Last House on Mulholland, Los Angeles, CA from Aquatic Zoo Tropical Fish, Thousand Oaks, CA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-118.840161 34.172588)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-118.320457 34.131243)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'cafe'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-118.840161 34.172588)',4326)::geography, 50000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-118.840161 34.172588)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
